Package com.tangosol.net.topic

Class Subscriber.Filtered<V>

java.lang.Object
com.tangosol.net.topic.Subscriber.Filtered<V>
Type Parameters:
V - the type of the value on the topic
All Implemented Interfaces:
ExternalizableLite, PortableObject, Subscriber.Option<V,V>, Serializable
Enclosing interface:
Subscriber<V>
public static class Subscriber.Filtered<V> extends Object implements Subscriber.Option<V,V>, ExternalizableLite, PortableObject
The Filtered option specifies a filter that will determine which topic values a subscriber is interested in receiving. Note that all members of a subscriber group share a single filter. If members join the group using different filters then the last one to join will set the filter for the group.
